{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8f92eb1fc4","title":"关于印经典著作大字本的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1e7e7d47b7","index":0,"year":1963,"month":8,"day":14,"articleId":"8f92eb1fc4"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"43843d5764","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"8f92eb1fc4","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央宣传部副部长周扬给毛泽东的请示报告上。周扬的报告说，规定干部阅读马思列斯经典著作的书目问题，已由陆定一同志主持召集会议讨论过一次，并初步拟定了一个书自，现已送请陈佰达审阅，最后商定后再报主席。印经典著作大学本事，出版方面同志的意见，以采用照相放大胶印为好。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6a3e637120","type":"title","text":"关于印经典著作大字本的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"8f92eb1fc4"},{"id":"43843d5764","type":"paragraph","text":"周扬同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"8f92eb1fc4"},{"id":"f13cfda2a6","type":"paragraph","text":"同意用照相放大胶印的办法。但请注意封面不用硬纸；大书（例如《唯物主义与经验批判主义》《反杜林论》）过去例作一卷或两卷，现应分装四卷或八卷，使每卷重量减轻","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"8f92eb1fc4"},{"id":"9cfc1b450d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"8f92eb1fc4"},{"id":"d2784473e7","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"8f92eb1fc4"}],"page":{"id":"eded74b807","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"8f92eb1fc4","start":511,"end":511}}}},"__N_SSG":true}